comments: Reath (POR) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Smith Jr.'s (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Reath (POR) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Replay review of the foul called on Brogdon (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Brogdon avoids making contact with Johnson's (BKN) arm prior to the release of the jump shot attempt. As there was no imminent possession at the time of the whistle, play resumes with a jump ball at center circle.
Replay review of the out of bounds called on Claxton (BKN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Claxton deflects the ball OOB.
Sharpe (POR) brings two hands toward Claxton's (BKN) body, affecting his SQBR following the rebound.
POR is awarded a timeout prior to 5 seconds elapsing.
Replay review of the out of bounds called on Simons (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Finney-Smith (BKN) steps out of bounds with his left foot prior to releasing the ball.
Claxton (BKN) moves alongside Sharpe's (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (BKN) and Simons (POR) momentarily come together and marginal contact occurs before the expiration of the game clock.
The game is stopped due to a game clock malfunction. After correcting the clock, the game correctly resumes with BKN retaining possession.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Simons' (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Grant (POR) is moving laterally toward Bridges' (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as the two come together during the drive.
Finney-Smith (BKN) initiates body contact with Sharpe (POR) that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Reath (POR) brings both arms around Claxton (BKN) and wraps him in the post.
Smith Jr. (BKN) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
Smith Jr. (BKN) is attempting to dislodge the ball and incidental follow-through arm contact occurs with Simons (POR).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Bridges (BKN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB.
